ABOUT US
/$
$
A Family Tradition
/$
$
The Crystal Bar is a casual neighborhood Bar located in the center of Zephyrhills. Opened in 1954 by Bob and Jerry, their children and grandchildren are carrying on the tradition of creating a fun and welcoming place for the community.
Whether you are taking advantage of our great daytime drink specials or nightly entertainment, allow yourself to unwind a bit and feel free to make a friend or two. After all, we’re more than just drinks, we’re a family. So what are you waiting for? Drop by!
